      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1101/2024.12.31.630944"
      },
      "sc:description": "The RTK Database provides curated information on Receptor Tyrosine Kinase (RTK) domains, including structural data, ligand-binding properties, and sequence information. It leverages experimentally-resolved structures and AlphaFold2 models to explore domain architecture and evolutionary relationships within the RTK superfamily.",
